<H3> <TI>   Magazine Issues Communique on Wiretapping Case </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Magazine Issues Communique on Wiretapping Case </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA1104151094 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 in Spanish 0000 GMT 7 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA1104151094 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 </F>

<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "24 Hours" newscast] </F>
  [Text] The controversy between the weekly magazine SEMANA 
and Julio Mario Santo Domingo over alleged wiretapping has not 
ended. SEMANA issued a communique today saying that it will wait 
for a ruling from the Colombian judicial authorities as this is 
not merely a case of gossip but a serious crime. 
  Santo Domingo had previously issued a communique denying a 
report published by the magazine linking him to an alleged case 
of wiretapping. 

</TEXT>

