  [Text] The final protocol of the conversations held this 
week by the joint commissions of Colombia and Cuba was signed on 
14 April at the headquarters of the State Committee for Economic 
Cooperation [CECE]. The agreement includes areas such as 
education, science and technology, culture, and sports, among 
